## Template: Change Integration

```json
{
  "name": "change_integration_workflow",
  "description": "Process and integrate requirement changes into existing project",
  "trigger_patterns": [
    "process changes",
    "integrate new requirements",
    "handle requirement updates",
    "merge requirement changes"
  ],
  "prerequisites": {
    "required": ["existing_project_structure", "change_source"],
    "optional": ["change_description", "impact_scope"]
  },
  "workflow": {
    "steps": [
      {
        "step": 1,
        "skill": "change-management",
        "purpose": "Document and classify incoming change",
        "inputs": ["change_source", "change_description"],
        "outputs": ["change-record.md"],
        "duration": "2-3 minutes",
        "critical": true
      },
      {
        "step": 2,
        "skill": "change-impact-analysis",
        "purpose": "Trace impact of change across hierarchy artifacts",
        "inputs": ["change-record.md", "hierarchy-root-folder"],
        "outputs": ["change-impact-report.md", "change-impact-report.json"],
        "flags": "--mode what-if (default); review output before switching to --mode apply",
        "duration": "3-5 minutes"
      },
      {
        "step": 3,
        "skill": "process-merge",
        "purpose": "Merge changes with existing requirements",
        "conditional": "if multiple requirement sources",
        "inputs": ["change_source", "existing_requirements.md"],
        "outputs": ["merged-requirements.md"],
        "duration": "3-5 minutes"
      },
      {
        "step": 4,
        "skill": "re_execute_affected_skills",
        "purpose": "Re-run skills affected by changes",
        "note": "Variable depending on change scope; use change-impact-report.json to identify affected skills",
        "inputs": ["change-impact-report.json"],
        "outputs": ["updated_artifacts"],
        "duration": "Variable"
      },
      {
        "step": 5,
        "skill": "project-status-reporting",
        "purpose": "Generate change impact summary",
        "inputs": ["change-record.md", "change-impact-report.md"],
        "outputs": ["change-summary.md"],
        "duration": "2-3 minutes"
      }
    ]
  },
  "success_criteria": [
    "Change properly documented",
    "Impact on existing work assessed", 
    "Affected artifacts updated",
    "Change integrated successfully"
  ],
  "estimated_total_duration": "Variable (10-30 minutes depending on scope)"
}
```

## Usage Instructions

### For EDPS Skill Navigator

1. **Template Selection**: Match user intent to appropriate template using trigger patterns
2. **Prerequisite Check**: Verify required inputs are available
3. **Dynamic Execution**: Follow workflow steps, handling conditionals and parallel opportunities
4. **Checkpoint Monitoring**: Verify success criteria at designated checkpoints
5. **Error Recovery**: Use failure actions when steps don't complete successfully

### Template Customization

Templates can be customized based on:
- **Project Context**: E-commerce vs. enterprise vs. academic projects
- **User Experience**: Novice vs. expert users
- **Time Constraints**: Quick vs. comprehensive analysis needs
- **Organizational Standards**: Company-specific workflow modifications

### Extension Points

New templates can be added for:
- **Industry-Specific Workflows**: Healthcare, finance, manufacturing domains
- **Methodology Integration**: Agile, waterfall, lean startup approaches  
- **Tool Integration**: Integration with specific external tools or systems
- **Quality Frameworks**: Integration with quality assurance or compliance requirements

---

**Template Version**: 2.0.0
**Last Updated**: 2026-03-16
**Compatible With**: EDPS Skill Navigator v1.2.0
**Format**: JSON with embedded workflow logic

## Template: Legacy Migration (C1 — hierarchy-management)

```json
{
  "name": "legacy_migration_workflow",
  "description": "Non-destructively upgrade flat (Project 1) collaboration diagrams to Project 3 hierarchical boundary format. Uses hierarchy-management --op migrate (migration-tools is deprecated).",
  "trigger_patterns": [
    "migrate diagrams",
    "upgrade legacy diagrams",
    "add boundaries to existing diagrams",
    "convert flat diagrams"
  ],
  "prerequisites": {
    "required": ["collaboration-diagrams.md"],
    "optional": ["collaboration-diagrams.json"]
  },
  "workflow": {
    "steps": [
      {
        "step": 1,
        "skill": "hierarchy-management",
        "op": "--op migrate --mode preview",
        "purpose": "Preview boundary and stereotype inferences without writing files",
        "inputs": ["collaboration-diagrams.md"],
        "outputs": ["migration-log.md (preview)"],
        "duration": "2-3 minutes",
        "critical": true
      },
      {
        "step": 2,
        "skill": "human-review",
        "purpose": "Review LOW-confidence participant stereotype assignments in migration-log.md",
        "note": "Manual step — approve or correct LOW-confidence participant type inferences",
        "duration": "5-15 minutes",
        "critical": true
      },
      {
        "step": 3,
        "skill": "hierarchy-management",
        "op": "--op migrate --mode apply",
        "purpose": "Write enhanced counterpart files",
        "inputs": ["collaboration-diagrams.md", "reviewed migration-log.md"],
        "outputs": ["collaboration-diagrams-enhanced.md", "collaboration-diagrams-enhanced.json", "migration-log.md"],
        "duration": "2-3 minutes",
        "critical": true
      },
      {
        "step": 4,
        "skill": "diagram-generatecollaboration",
        "op": "--mode boundary-validate",
        "purpose": "Validate VR-1 through VR-4 on enhanced diagrams",
        "inputs": ["collaboration-diagrams-enhanced.md"],
        "outputs": ["boundary-validation-report.json"],
        "duration": "2-3 minutes",
        "critical": false
      },
      {
        "step": 5,
        "skill": "hierarchy-management",
        "op": "--op decompose",
        "purpose": "Optionally decompose control-type participants in enhanced diagrams",
        "conditional": "if user wants to create Level N+1 sub-processes",
        "inputs": ["collaboration-diagrams-enhanced.md"],
        "outputs": ["[NN]-[Name]Boundary/ sub-process folders"],
        "duration": "3-5 minutes per participant",
        "critical": false
      }
    ]
  },
  "success_criteria": [
    "Flat diagrams upgraded to boundary-annotated format",
    "All participant types assigned (HIGH or MEDIUM confidence)",
    "VR-1 through VR-4 boundary validation passes",
    "Original files unchanged"
  ],
  "estimated_total_duration": "15-25 minutes"
}
```

## Template: Full Analysis-to-Planning Pipeline

```json
{
  "name": "full_analysis_to_planning_pipeline",
  "description": "Canonical end-to-end EDPS workflow from raw requirements through to an approved project schedule. Sequence is phase-locked; phases 1-3 must complete before phase 4 begins.",
  "trigger_patterns": [
    "full pipeline",
    "analysis to planning",
    "end-to-end workflow",
    "complete EDPS workflow",
    "run everything"
  ],
  "prerequisites": {
    "required": ["requirements_document"],
    "optional": ["existing_orgModel"]
  },
  "phases": [
    {
      "phase": 1,
      "name": "Project Setup",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 1,
          "skill": "project-document-management",
          "purpose": "Create standardized project folder tree",
          "inputs": ["project_name", "project_number"],
          "outputs": ["project-folder-tree"],
          "critical": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "phase": 2,
      "name": "Requirements Processing",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 2,
          "skill": "requirements-merge",
          "purpose": "Merge multiple requirement sources into unified spec",
          "conditional": "if more than one requirements source",
          "inputs": ["requirements_documents"],
          "outputs": ["unified-requirements.md"]
        },
        {
          "step": 3,
          "skill": "requirements-ingest",
          "purpose": "Normalize requirements into atomic chunks with IDs",
          "inputs": ["requirements_document OR unified-requirements.md"],
          "outputs": ["requirements.md", "requirements.json"],
          "critical": true
        },
        {
          "step": 4,
          "skill": "goals-extract",
          "purpose": "Extract business goals, KPIs, constraints",
          "inputs": ["requirements.md"],
          "outputs": ["goals.md", "goals.json"],
          "parallel_with": [5],
          "critical": true
        },
        {
          "step": 5,
          "skill": "process-w5h",
          "purpose": "W5H contextual analysis",
          "inputs": ["requirements.md"],
          "outputs": ["w5h-analysis.md", "w5h-analysis.json"],
          "parallel_with": [4]
        },
        {
          "step": 6,
          "skill": "process-scopemin",
          "purpose": "Identify MVP scope boundaries",
          "inputs": ["requirements.md", "goals.json"],
          "outputs": ["scope-analysis.md", "scope-analysis.json"]
        }
      ],
      "parallel_opportunities": [
        {
          "steps": [4, 5],
          "note": "goals-extract and process-w5h can run concurrently after requirements-ingest"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "phase": 3,
      "name": "Domain Analysis",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 7,
          "skill": "domain-extractconcepts",
          "purpose": "Identify domain entities and relationships",
          "inputs": ["requirements.md", "w5h-analysis.md"],
          "outputs": ["domain-concepts.md", "domain-concepts.json"],
          "critical": true
        },
        {
          "step": 8,
          "skill": "domain-alignentities",
          "purpose": "Align with organizational domain standards",
          "inputs": ["domain-concepts.md"],
          "outputs": ["domain-alignment.md", "domain-alignment.json"]
        },
        {
          "step": 9,
          "skill": "domain-proposenewconcepts",
          "purpose": "Propose domain extensions for coverage gaps",
          "inputs": ["domain-alignment.md"],
          "outputs": ["domain-newconcepts.md"]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "phase": 4,
      "name": "Design & Visualization",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 10,
          "skill": "diagram-generatecollaboration",
          "purpose": "Generate EDPS collaboration diagrams with boundary syntax",
          "inputs": ["domain-concepts.json", "requirements.json"],
          "outputs": ["collaboration-diagrams.md", "collaboration-diagrams.json", "boundary-validation-report.json"],
          "critical": true
        },
        {
          "step": 11,
          "skill": "hierarchy-management",
          "op": "--op decompose",
          "purpose": "Decompose control-type participants into Level N+1 sub-processes",
          "inputs": ["collaboration-diagrams.md"],
          "outputs": ["[NN]-[Name]Boundary/ stub sub-process folders", "hierarchy-metadata.json"]
        },
        {
          "step": 12,
          "skill": "documentation-automation",
          "purpose": "Generate content-complete docs for each hierarchy node",
          "inputs": ["[process-folder]/collaboration.md per node"],
          "outputs": ["main.md", "process.md", "collaboration.md", "domain-model.md (per node)"]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "phase": 5,
      "name": "Process & Change Management",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 13,
          "skill": "process-merge",
          "purpose": "Merge new process model with org process models",
          "inputs": ["collaboration-diagrams.md"],
          "outputs": ["merged-process-model.md"]
        },
        {
          "step": 14,
          "skill": "process-findtopandupdate",
          "purpose": "Update top-level requirements from analysis insights",
          "inputs": ["merged-process-model.md", "domain-alignment.md"],
          "outputs": ["updated-top-requirements.md"]
        },
        {
          "step": 15,
          "skill": "change-impact-analysis",
          "purpose": "Assess blast radius of proposed model changes",
          "inputs": ["change description", "hierarchy-root-folder"],
          "outputs": ["change-impact-report.md", "change-impact-report.json"],
          "parallel_with": [14],
          "conditional": "if changes detected"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "phase": 6,
      "name": "Model Integration",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 16,
          "skill": "model-integration",
          "purpose": "Integrate new domain models into org model structure",
          "inputs": ["domain-alignment.json", "domain-concepts.json", "orgModel root"],
          "outputs": ["integrated-model-update.md"]
        },
        {
          "step": 17,
          "skill": "orgmodel-update",
          "purpose": "Update orgModel documents (EDPS-Hierarchy Guard applies)",
          "inputs": ["integrated-model-update.md"],
          "outputs": ["vocabulary.md", "test-case-list.md (updated)"]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "phase": 7,
      "name": "Planning",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 18,
          "skill": "plan-derivetasks",
          "purpose": "Convert requirements into actionable tasks",
          "inputs": ["requirements.md", "scope-analysis.md"],
          "outputs": ["task-breakdown.md", "task-breakdown.json"],
          "critical": true
        },
        {
          "step": 19,
          "skill": "plan-estimateeffort",
          "purpose": "PERT-based effort estimation per task",
          "inputs": ["task-breakdown.json"],
          "outputs": ["effort-estimates.md", "effort-estimates.json"]
        },
        {
          "step": 20,
          "skill": "plan-buildschedule",
          "purpose": "Build Gantt schedule with critical path",
          "inputs": ["task-breakdown.json", "effort-estimates.json"],
          "outputs": ["project-schedule.md", "project-schedule.json"]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "phase": 8,
      "name": "Validation & Reporting",
      "steps": [
        {
          "step": 21,
          "skill": "hierarchy-validation",
          "purpose": "Authoritative structural integrity check (pre-condition for edps-compliance)",
          "inputs": ["orgModel root"],
          "outputs": ["hierarchy-validation-report.md", "hierarchy-validation-report.json"],
          "critical": true
        },
        {
          "step": 22,
          "skill": "edps-compliance",
          "purpose": "Full EDPS methodology compliance check (VR-1-4, HR-2/6, EP-1-4)",
          "inputs": ["orgModel root", "hierarchy-validation-report.json"],
          "outputs": ["edps-compliance-report.md", "edps-compliance-report.json"]
        },
        {
          "step": 23,
          "skill": "integration-testing",
          "purpose": "End-to-end skill workflow validation",
          "inputs": ["all project artifacts"],
          "outputs": ["integration-test-report.md"]
        },
        {
          "step": 24,
          "skill": "project-status-reporting",
          "purpose": "Generate executive / engineering status dashboard",
          "inputs": ["tasks/task-tracking.md", "project-plan.md"],
          "outputs": ["status-report.md"]
        }
      ],
      "parallel_opportunities": [
        {
          "steps": [22, 23],
          "note": "edps-compliance and integration-testing can run concurrently after hierarchy-validation passes"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "global_parallel_opportunities": [
    {
      "steps": [4, 5],
      "phase": 2,
      "note": "goals-extract || process-w5h after requirements-ingest"
    },
    {
      "steps": [14, 15],
      "phase": 5,
      "note": "process-findtopandupdate || change-impact-analysis (if changes detected)"
    },
    {
      "steps": [22, 23],
      "phase": 8,
      "note": "edps-compliance || integration-testing (after hierarchy-validation)"
    }
  ],
  "success_criteria": [
    "Project structure initialised",
    "Requirements atomised with IDs and traceability",
    "Domain model complete and aligned",
    "EDPS collaboration diagrams with boundary annotations generated",
    "Hierarchy decomposed and documented",
    "Org model updated without hierarchy conflicts",
    "Task breakdown, effort estimates, and schedule approved",
    "hierarchy-validation exits VALID or MOSTLY_VALID",
    "edps-compliance score ≥ 80 %"
  ],
  "estimated_total_duration": "2-4 hours (with human review gates)"
}
```